verbose_text: Thus, TRIM5alpha mediated post-entry restriction is thought to have at least two phases : (i) TRIM5alpha induces rapid disassembly of viral core in a proteasome dependent manner and (ii) TRIM5alpha degrades HIV-1 cDNAs in a proteasome independent manner.
evidence: TRIM5alpha induces rapid disassembly of viral core in a proteasome-dependent manner and (ii) TRIM5alpha degrades HIV-1 cDNAs in a proteasome
